edu.frontrange.csc240.a8

Class Model

  • Object
    • java.util.Observable
      • edu.frontrange.csc240.a8.Model

  • public class Model
extends java.util.Observable
    This class acts as the “model” for the computation of the temperatures, in the MVC (model-view-controller) design pattern used here to create this application. All of the information about temperatures to be converted is contained in this class.

    The model uses the Scale class to do the actual conversions between the source temperature scale and the target temperature scale.

    Version:
    2.0, 2016-10-15, Assignment 8, Exercise 12.13
    Author:
    Dr. Bruce K. Haddon, Instructor
